HypoDD interface (for large dataset):
1. Files
  (1) config file
    config.py
    hypodd.inp
  (2) format transfer
    mk_sta.py
    reloc2csv.py
  (3) main
    run_ph2dt.sh
    run_hypoDD.sh

2. Usage
  (1) Set parameters
    i/o paths & ph2dt_cc params in config.py
    hypoDD params in hypoDD.inp
  (2) run main
    sh run_ph2dt_cc
    sh run_hypoDD

